      { id: 320, question: "In a 0.1 M weak acid solution, [HвЃє] is:", options: ["Equal to 0.1 M", "Greater than 0.1 M", "Less than 0.1 M", "Zero"], answer: 2, explanation: "Partial dissociation of a weak acid gives [HвЃє] less than the initial acid concentration." }
