      { id: 350, question: "A solution has [HвЃє] = 3.2 Г— 10вЃ»вЃґ M. Approximate pH is:", options: ["~2", "~3", "~3.5", "~4"], answer: 2, explanation: "pH = -log(3.2 Г— 10вЃ»вЃґ) в‰€ 3.5." }
