      { id: 460, question: "Contact process for Hв‚‚SOв‚„ uses which catalyst?", options: ["Iron", "Platinum", "Vanadium(V) oxide (Vв‚‚Oв‚…)", "Nickel"], answer: 2, explanation: "The Contact process oxidises SOв‚‚ to SOв‚ѓ using vanadium(V) oxide catalyst." }
